
Smart Irrigation System (Root-Level Monitoring)
Project Title
Smart Root-Level Irrigation System
Problem
Traditional irrigation wastes water because plants are watered uniformly without checking moisture at the root level.
Solution
A system that monitors soil moisture near plant roots and automatically activates irrigation when needed.
Features
* Soil moisture monitoring
* Automatic water pump control
* IoT monitoring dashboard
* Water usage optimization
Components
* Soil Moisture Sensor
* Microcontroller (Arduino/ESP8266)
* Water Pump
* Relay Module
* WiFi Module
* Power Supply
